			<div class="featured-img-container">
			<img class="story-img" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/audre-lorde-image.png" title="A Timeless Take on Autobiography: Audre Lorde’s <em>Zami: A New Spelling of My Name</em>">
